phrases: Are you familiar with the phrase eighth-grader syndrome?
Children are most prone to it around the end of the eighth grade.
It is an adorable, yet dreadful disease resulting from new-found self-awareness
mixing with an overly active imagination
that results in the peculiar behavior we are all quite painfully familiar with.
Like the guy who only read weekly manga mags up until yesterday,
then suddenly starts reading the original English versions of books.
Or someone who has absolutely no idea what coffee tastes like,
but still tries to develop a taste for drinking it black.
And then there is those who believe that they possess special powers,
and become obsessed with the occult stuff overnight...
this boy was a textbook example of eighth-grader syndrome too.
He named himself the Dark Flame Master, and his catchphrase was...
Vanish into the embrace of dark flames!
That is so, so, so, so embarrassing!
makes one want to disappear from the surface of the Earth.
I will throw it all out later, so do not worry.
But you bought this one with the money you got from New Year's...
Can you just leave it alone?
I remember you declaring you would rule the world with this, though.
You used to wear that weird coat a lot back then too.
If I can live without remembering that, so can you!
Mom, it is Yuuta's entrance ceremony today.
Parents do not usually attend high school entrance ceremonies anyway.
Judging from her uniform, she goes to the same high school as me.
For some reason I got on a later train!
I do not know anyone here.
I intentionally chose a different high school to everyone else from my junior high.
The first impression is the most important!
I can never loose this cursed bandage from my arm, and for good reason.
Doing so would unleash the Black Flame Dragon on this world.
I have been on my own in that class ever since.
Do not worry about the past!
No one here knows me from back then!
I am the Dark Flame Master!
Perish, enveloped in the flames of darkness!
Could you spare me some pencil lead?
Which junior high are you from?
That is quite far from here.
Yeah, there is no one else from my old school here.
Yeah, I hardly know anyone too.
Hooray for my high school debut!
Say, how do you like the girls in this class?
Nice collection of hotties, do not you think so?
Pretty sweet, if you ask me.
Oh, she is in my class?
She is easily in first place on my list.
I crossed the pits of Hell to meet you here!
Dude, she just confessed to you!
No, you are getting it all wrong!
Yeah, I am sure she is...
The nurse had to go somewhere, so I was told to give you these eyedrops.
Hurry up or we will be late for the opening ceremony.
You were the one on my balcony last night, right?
Indeed, our paths once crossed, measureless eons before this age.
The moment I saw you, my Wicked Eye revealed to me our destiny.
That is why I sought the chance to meet you once again.
Doubtlessly, this is the work of the Cult of Darkness.
Do I need any more proof?
The Wicked Eye wields darkness tamed by the power of a pure heart.
As it itself is defiled by darkness, it cannot endure anything pure, such as holy water.
We almost fell victim to the enemy's schemes.
We must be more careful from now on,
Be enveloped by the flames of darkness!
Where did you hear about it?
My Wicked Eye is perfectly clairvoyant.
I know everything about level 7 warlocks and their powe
Where did you hear about it?
The entirety of the future and the past is but an open book before
Where did you hear about it?
I asked where you heard about it!
It was at the gym earlier!
I thought no one was listening...
Not a word to anyone about this, got it?!
The principles of the Deep Horizon and the composition changes in
I am talking about my past!
No wielder of the flames of darkness!
I decided to leave all that behind me when I graduated!
Every single tiny little bit of it!
So you are now a level 8 warlock?!
I am talking about eighth-grader syndrome!
I am not the Dark Flame Master or any kind of warlock!
I am just a normal high school freshman!
Let me tell you a secret: you are an average high school freshman too!
Not that it even exists in the first place.
Do you want to see my eye?
You have got to be kidding me!
I will put it back in.
It is just a colored contact?
Oh no... I can feel it... inside me...
I will tell you one more time: I left that crap behind me.
So do not come anywhere near me!
And shut up about the past!
But you have seen my eye.
The contract between us is complete.
We share the heart of darkness.
And now for the freshman address.
If that weirdo latched onto me like that, there must still be something off about me.
This beautiful spring day with all the cherry trees in full blossom
is the day we join the community of this school.
Representing all freshmen, I would like to give words of gratitude for this grand ceremony.
Now that we are done with the introductions, let us call it a day.
Please be sure to check your schedule when you get home.
A few of us were talking about going for lunch together.
The girl you took to the nurse's earlier.
Did you promise her you would walk home together?
I want nothing to do with her!
You do not swing that way?
I just do not want weird rumors to spread.
She just moved here, so she does not know the town.
It looks like you live very close to each other.
You live on the floor above me?
I will come next time for sure!
So when did you move in?
I thought the only person up there was some office lady living on her own.
I changed residences the day before yesterday.
So you moved in with your sister.
Or rather, that is what we lead others to believe.
But she is actually a powerful sorceress who oversees the Deep Horizon.
When she awakens her powers, I am no match for her.
Even if I use my Wicked Eye.
I am not surprised she gets mad at you with all the nonsense you keep going on about.
With the power of the Dark Flame Master,
we could break through the Overseers' barrier and find the Deep Horizon!
I have come up with a new attack for you!
And if I am wearing these and the enemy attacks...
I broke a few of my ribs...
What do you mean, B, A?
The Overseers are pulling the strings from the shadows.
Do you accept my powers now?
By the way, B and A stand for banana and apple.
It differs by the season, so be careful.
Could you stop wasting my time?
They meant to deliver these to Ms. Takanashi,
but she was not at home, so they asked me to take care of it for her.
I returned home late due to the Overseers' interference.
I should have been home by three according to pl
Why do you have so much stuff?
It is way too much for one person.
Do not tell me it is all junk like that!
I will go and get dinner ready.
There are many useful items here.
It can be used as a weapon...
You are just as pretty as your sister!
Umm, what happened to your eye?
There is nothing wrong with it or anything.
The Wicked Eye harnesses darkness using sacred powe
Yumeha, do not take that out around h Ow!
If you slung that over your back, it would be perfect!
He wore a black coat, had that on his back...
He certainly had some strange ideas back then.
Always chanting spells or whatever those were before meals...
Mom, is not it time you left for your night shift?
I told them it was trash, and they just go rummaging through it anyway...
That is the life of the Dark Flame Master.
Like I said, I left that all behind me.
There is no such thing as the Flames of Darkness or the Power of the Dark Dragon.
Vanish into the embrace of dark flames!
I just thought they would be too valuable to just throw away.
I will make some money by putting them up for auction instead.
You will catch a cold if you stand out here too long.
spring was actually quite warm this year.
